Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.athenaeum.Book
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is a class of book objects that have an ISBN, author, title, status, and owner, and may also have a description and/or photo.
